*''A Study of the Acooli Language'' (1938)
*''The Lwoo'' (1950–54)
*''Zur Gesellschaft und Religion der Nueer'' (1953)
*''A Study of the Logbara (Ma'di) Language'' (1960)
*''A Study of the Pokot (Suk) Language'' (1978)
